The below services facilitate payments in Bitcoins. Different from exchanges Bitcoins are treaded as means of payment and not as financial good. Different from eWallets the provided services do not aim to store Bitcoins and facilitate transfers between individuals but to provide smooth Bitcoin payments.

* [[!img "BIPS.gif" size=20x20 link=https://bips.me]] [BIPS](https://bips.me) ([[info|BIPS]]), Bitcoin merchant solutions, point of sale system, mobile checkout, currency conversion and withdraw to bank account in the merchants local currency to any country.
* [BitKassa](https://www.BitKassa.nl) Bitcoin payment solution, customer pays bitcoins - merchant gets euro, can be 100% euro or percentage bitcoin/euro. No fee (NL).
* [Coinvoy](https://coinvoy.net) free payment gateway API for cryptocurrencies, featuring escrow and auto-exchange
* [BitPay](http://www.BitPay.com) ([[info|BitPay]]), merchant payment processing system
* [BitUtils Merchant](http://merchant.bitutils.com) BitUtils Merchant solution enables merchants to accept bitcoins with simple HTML buttons. No programming or server admin skills required. 0.5% fee for incoming BTCs.
* [Coinbase](http://coinbase.com) Provide online merchant services. 
* [[!img "Coinkite.gif" size=20x20 link=https://coinkite.com/promo/beginners]] [Coinkite](https://coinkite.com/promo/beginners) Provide merchant solutions and hardware Point of Sale terminal. 
* [[!img "PikaPay_Logo.png" size=27x27 link=https://PikaPay.com]][PikaPay](https://PikaPay.com) ([[info|PikaPay]]) Send and receive payments to any Twitter account.
* [BitVendor](http://www.bitvendor.net),  Bitcoin, Cash, and Debit Card Point of Sale System
* [The BFG Program](http://bfg.swfchan.com/?start) (Bitcoins For Gets) - Link to swfchan.com and earn bitcoins
* [[!img "gocoin-logo.png" title="alt=GoCoin" link=http://www.gocoin.com]] [[GoCoin]] International Payment Processing for Bitcoin
* [BitcoinPay](http://bitcoinpay.com) ([[info|Bitcoinpay]]), Payment gateway on Bitcoin network for merchants in Europe [CZK, EUR, USD](PLN,).
* [Coin For Coffee](http://coinforcoffee.com) Provides in-store payment with bitcoin at retailers(Currently Starbucks and expanding to other stores in US, CAN, UK.
